It feels this location has more consistent quality for breakfast compared to the North Road location. When its busy it feels understaffed so you cannot expect a speedy service (its not the staffs fault) -- its a small operation. They often dont seem to have certain items (ice cream etc) so youll need to go elsewhere for that. The staff dont need to serve the drive-thru crowd so thats a plus

I do believe that a lot of these people are rightful in their claims, but one thing everyone needs to understand for wherever they go is to not put so much blame on ALL of the employees because of one experience of ONE employee or manager.
